<item>
            <title>[SPARK-3090]  Avoid not stopping SparkContext with YARN Client mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-3090</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we use YARN Cluster mode, ApplicationMaser register a shutdown hook, stopping SparkContext.&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks to this, SparkContext can stop even if Application forgets to stop SparkContext itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But, unfortunately, YARN Client mode doesn&apos;t have such mechanism.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12734657">SPARK-3090</key>
            <summary> Avoid not stopping SparkContext with YARN Client mode</summary>
